Us rabbits want to strive for transparency within our community, as there have been far too many rug-pulls in this ecosystem. We as a team want to make a positive lasting impact on the whole entire SOL environment. A hefty portion of the mint proceeds will go towards creating CUSTOM merchandise for holders who receive an NFT with a ticket in the top left corner. A substantial portion of revenue will also be used to donate to a charity decided upon by the Rakish Rabbits community!
